metadata.title: xo, Fetti Bachelorette Party Drink Pouches - 16 count | Bachelorette Party Cups, Bridesmaid Names Decorations, Maid of Dishonor Favors, Miss Behaving
features: Cheers! Our 16 pack drink pouches are the party addition you've been looking for + a guaranteed hit!
Squad Approved: have fun choosing between 8 different designs - there's 2 each per design!
Spill Proof: say goodbye to spills with our resealable pouches; each pouch comes with a pink straw :)
Same Drink Pouches Forever: get ready to use these pouches again + again! They're made of durable BPA-free material and can hold up to 15 oz of your drink of choice!
Cute Stuff Inside: and outside, too! Every set comes gift-ready for your favorite Bride-to-Be's bach party!
description: Sip sip hooray! Spill-proof your drinks with our clear pouches w/ text and gold foil - 16 reusable ones to be exact! Leave no babe behind with these drink pouches set that comes with 2 each of 8 different designs including "Shot Queen", "Maid of Dishonor", "Miss Behaving" and more ! We also give you full permission to use them again + again - they're made out of durable BPA-free material, so why not?! Refills are totally encouraged ;) These Bach Names Drink Pouches are truly the ultimate bachelorette party decoration!
